00:36:23,170 --> 00:36:27,430
♫ The silhouettes of the concrete jungle ♫

476
00:36:27,430 --> 00:36:30,690
♫ All I see is you ♫

477
00:36:30,690 --> 00:36:35,240
Zheng Xiao'en, who are you exactly?

478
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:38,470
♫ Streetlights awaiting dusk ♫

479
00:36:38,470 --> 00:36:40,710
♫ Watching for the next morning ♫

480
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:43,880
♫ Nothing is impossible ♫

481
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:48,560
♫ Even if no one is perfect ♫

482
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,980
Who are you exactly?

483
00:36:52,290 --> 00:36:56,400
Why is my name on that lantern?

484
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:59,460
Why do you keep appearing before my eyes?

485
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:04,270
I...

486
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:12,530
Who else could I be?

487
00:37:12,530 --> 00:37:15,960
I'm Zheng Xiao'en, someone who works at a publishing company.

488
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:21,160
[Ruge Publishing]

489
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:25,860
♫ All of the innocent romance was lost to you ♫

490
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:29,210
♫ If you were a painter ♫

491
00:37:29,210 --> 00:37:31,220
♫ Then I'll be your canvas ♫

492
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:32,510
It is all your fault.

493
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:34,380
Why did you bring Tianxing here to pray?

494
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:36,550
Do you think Tianxing has nothing better to do?

495
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:39,820
My grandfather said Mazu is very powerful.

496
00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:45,450
Also, weren’t you the one who said that the CEO has had bad luck recently?

497
00:37:45,450 --> 00:37:47,910
I just want to help the CEO change his luck.

498
00:37:47,910 --> 00:37:51,260
Change his luck? Now he's attracting evil spirits!

499
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:53,960
So much for changing his luck.

500
00:37:55,150 --> 00:37:57,460
Actually, there's something I haven't told you.

501
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:59,460
What?

